title: SET_VEHICLE_DIRT_LEVEL
content:
0x2B39128B// SetVehicleDirtLevel
void SET_VEHICLE_DIRT_LEVEL(Vehicle vehicle, float dirtLevel);Parameters:vehicle: The vehicle to set.dirtLevel: A number between 0.0 and 15.0 representing the vehicles dirt level.Sets the dirt level of the passed vehicle.This is the server-side RPC native equivalent of the client native SET_VEHICLE_DIRT_LEVEL.
